《[[乾吧！我的彩虹人生|乾吧！我的彩虹人生]]》是一部由{{tsl|en|Shonali Bose|邵娜莉·玻色}}执导的印度[[剧情片|剧情片]]。导演玻色在多伦多国际电影节上获得[[亚洲电影促进联盟|亚洲影评人联盟奖]]。<ref name="netpac">{{cite web|last1=Kannan|first1=Indira|title=Margarita, with a Straw wins NETPAC Award at Toronto film fest|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/margarita-with-a-straw-toronto-film-festival-netpac-award-kalki-koechlin-sayani-gupta-shonali-bose-nilesh-maniyar-292709-2014-09-16|work=India Today|accessdate=2018-01-15|date=2014-09-16|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180115185531/https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/margarita-with-a-straw-toronto-film-festival-netpac-award-kalki-koechlin-sayani-gupta-shonali-bose-nilesh-maniyar-292709-2014-09-16|archivedate=2018-01-15}}</ref>之后该片还分别获得塔林黑夜电影节观众奖与沃苏勒亚洲国际电影节青年评审团奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Kalki-Koechlins-film-Margarita-With-A-Straw-wins-two-awards-at-the-Vesoul-Film-Festival/articleshow/46452929.cms|title=Kalki Koechlin's film Margarita with a Straw wins two awards at the Vesoul Film Festival|work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|accessdate=2018-01-07|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228233400/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Kalki-Koechlins-film-Margarita-With-A-Straw-wins-two-awards-at-the-Vesoul-Film-Festival/articleshow/46452929.cms|archivedate=2017-12-28}}</ref><ref name="tallinn">{{Cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Kalki-bags-top-honors-at-Tallinn-Film-Festival/articleshow/45318690.cms |title=Kalki bags top honors at Tallinn Film Festival |date=2014-11-29 |work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |access-date=2016-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180228093344/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com//entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Kalki-bags-top-honors-at-Tallinn-Film-Festival/articleshow/45318690.cms |archive-date=2018-02-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>柯切林也凭借其在剧中的表现获得塔林电影节最佳女演员奖，{{tsl|en|Screen_Awards|Screen Award for Best Actress|荧屏奖最佳女演员}}以及{{tsl|en|63rd National Film Awards|第63届印度国家电影奖}}{{tsl|en|National Film Award – Special Jury Award (feature film)|评审团特别奖}}。<ref name="nationalaward">{{cite news |url=http://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/amitabh-kangana-bag-national-awards/article8404825.ece |title=Live: Amitabh, Kangana bag national awards |date=2013-03-28 |work=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]] |accessdate=2018-01-08 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328065341/http://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/amitabh-kangana-bag-national-awards/article8404825.ece |archivedate=2016-03-28 }}</ref><ref name="2016screen">{{cite web |url=http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/screen-awards-2016-complete-list-of-winners-1263815 |title=Screen Awards 2016: Complete List of Winners |date=2016-01-09 |publisher=[[NDTV|NDTV]] |accessdate=2018-01-08 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160110051251/http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/screen-awards-2016-complete-list-of-winners-1263815 |archivedate=2016-01-10 }}</ref>而她也获得{{tsl|en|Seattle International Film Festival|西雅图国际电影节}}及[[亚洲电影大奖|亚洲电影大奖]]最佳女演员的提名。<ref name=":0">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/seattle-international-film-festival-winners-800668 |title='The Dark Horse' Wins Top Honor at Seattle Film Fest |date=2015-07-06 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |last1=Kilday |first1=Gregg |accessdate=2017-05-03 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222103426/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/seattle-international-film-festival-winners-800668 |archivedate=2015-12-22 }}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/asian-film-awards-2015-haider-bags-four-nominations-kalki-koechlin-nominated-best-actress-624676 |title=Asian Film Awards 2015: 'Haider' Bags Four Nominations; Kalki Koechlin Nominated for Best Actress Category |date=2015-02-26 |work=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] |last1=Mehta |first1=Ankit |accessdate=2016-01-24 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926182022/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/asian-film-awards-2015-haider-bags-four-nominations-kalki-koechlin-nominated-best-actress-624676 |archivedate=2015-09-26 }}</ref>麦克雷利则在[[亚洲电影大奖|亚洲电影大奖]]上获得最佳原创音乐奖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/movies/kalki-koechlins-margarita-with-a-straw-wins-at-asian-film-awards_1568241.html |title=Kalki Koechlin's 'Margarita with a Straw' wins at Asian Film Awards |publisher={{tsl|en|Zee News||Zee News}} |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180115173610/http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/movies/kalki-koechlins-margarita-with-a-straw-wins-at-asian-film-awards_1568241.html |archive-date=2018-01-15 |access-date=2018-01-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/kalki-koechlin-starrer-margarita-straw-becomes-only-indian-film-win-asian-film-awards-627307 |title=Kalki Koechlin Starrer 'Margarita with a Straw' Becomes Only Indian Film to Win Asian Film Awards [Photos+Winners' List] |date=2015-03-26 |website=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180115174759/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/kalki-koechlin-starrer-margarita-straw-becomes-only-indian-film-win-asian-film-awards-627307 |archive-date=2018-01-15 |dead-url=yes |accessdate=2020-10-07 }}</ref>
